{"tid":2067371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人認同中國人身份跌至新低","createTime":"2020-06-17T03:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T03:44:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b23b73dac172de10978212d25c3927ca6cc6ac","tid":2067371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200617/ZGTDZSVQ2Q763AH5JZNNE7N3FU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2FZGTDZSVQ2Q763AH5JZNNE7N3FU%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7381ade7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2FZGTDZSVQ2Q763AH5JZNNE7N3FU%2F&h=95c46c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200617/ZGTDZSVQ2Q763AH5JZNNE7N3FU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港人認同中國人身份跌至新低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5P4Z6HFHXFLNWH5LVSUMCDFIFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5P4Z6HFHXFLNWH5LVSUMCDFIFA.jpg&h=bbb18b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有調查顯示，港人對「中國人」的認同感跌至1997年新低，評分為5.74分。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【香港民研】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥說，香港沒有國安法對中國14億人是一個風險。不過調查顯示，港人對這個國家的「安全」並未很在意。香港民意研究計劃的香港市民身份認同調查結果發現，港人對「中華民族一分子」及「中國人」的認同感分別創下2007年及1997年新低。<br />\n<br />\n民研計劃本月初由真實訪問員以隨機抽樣電話方式訪問1,002名香港居民，要求受訪者為不同身份認同感作出獨立評分。結果顯示，受訪者對「中國人」的認同感評分為5.74分，創下1997年開始有這項調查以來的最低評分；「中華民族一分子」的評分亦僅得6.25分，是2007年以來的新低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者：不可只靠灌輸<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：777批鬥公僕罷工 被轟違憲<br />\n<br />\n相反，受訪者對「香港人」的身份認同明顯較高，最新評分為8.57分，評分與去年6月一次調查同樣處於歷史高位。公務員事務。。。。。。。。。。。。。。同評分僅得4.9分，較對上一次調查下跌0.35分。<br />\n<br />\n港大心理學系副教授陳濬靈指出，數據反映，自我認同是「香港人」多於「中國人」受訪者不只是年輕人，當中30至49歲較年長的香港人有上升趨勢。他認為。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於國安法對民調工作的影響，香港民意調查研究所主席鍾庭耀說：「我哋會假定無罪咁繼續工作，除非有人話我哋知做緊嘅嘢違法。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者許湖洪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BWIGEUNKN7ZDE5LDOBWUBL7PCA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBWIGEUNKN7ZDE5LDOBWUBL7PCA.gif&h=b658b29c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02e163d884e59cf309559a91c124f4b61564eef8","tid":2067371,"uid":168394,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:03:18.000Z","msg":"咁都仲有5分 移民算 無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862c1a06d92c3e47966e90e60f2c6afc96bd1bce","tid":2067371,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02e163d884e59cf309559a91c124f4b61564eef8","tid":2067371,"uid":168394,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:03:18.000Z","msg":"咁都仲有5分 移民算 無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6632d2b5e84f9d54104744150adeff34d8c14818","tid":2067371,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:09:51.000Z","msg":"聽完蕭生講回鶻人個實況，有少少羞恥心都唔敢認啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347d5a1901c0c961937ad6b6dd9edbc8d43bd4ad","tid":2067371,"uid":12554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5b23b73dac172de10978212d25c3927ca6cc6ac","tid":2067371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200617/ZGTDZSVQ2Q763AH5JZNNE7N3FU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2FZGTDZSVQ2Q763AH5JZNNE7N3FU%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7381ade7\" data-e